GettheCountryInfo.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {

        try {

			var responseCountry = countryReq.execute();

            var httpStatusCountry = responseCountry.getStatusCode();

        } catch (ex) {
            var message = ex.message;
        }

    },

    type: 'GettheCountryInfo'
});
